trait.text:
You have a keen eyesight, especially in the dark. You can see in dim light within 120 feet of you as
                if it were bright light, and in darkness as if it were dim light. You can’t discern color in darkness,
                only shades of gray.

You have a keen eyesight, especially in the dark. You can see in dim light within 120 feet of you as
                if it were bright light, and in darkness as if it were dim light. You can’t discern color in darkness,
                only shades of gray.
